OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776618353
OL,3,CDriver who left scene of crash dies
OL,4,Cafter being hit by lorry on A1(M)
OL,6,FA van driver who walked away from his
OL,7,Fvehicle following a crash died 20
OL,8,Fminutes later after being hit by a
OL,9,Florry on a motorway.
OL,11,FThe 60-year-old, from Leeds, was in a
OL,12,FToyota Proace City van that was
OL,13,Finvolved in a collision with a white
OL,14,FRenault Captur on Valley Road in
OL,15,FDarrington, West Yorkshire, at 7.16am
OL,16,Fon Thursday.
OL,18,FWest Yorkshire Police said he "left
OL,19,Fthe area on foot" and was seen at
OL,20,Fabout 7.36am walking on the hard
OL,21,Fshoulder of the A1(M).
