OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776618353
OL,3,CDriver who left scene of crash dies
OL,4,Cafter being hit by lorry on A1(M)
OL,6,FA short time later he was hit by a
OL,7,Florry near the Ferrybridge junction.
OL,8,FHe died at the scene.
OL,10,FThe motorway was closed for much of
OL,11,Fthe day for investigations.
OL,13,FDet Insp Daniel Ridgway said: "This is
OL,14,Fa tragic incident in which a man has
OL,15,Flost his life. His family are aware
OL,16,Fand are being offered specialist
OL,17,Fsupport.
