OL,3,CDriver who left scene of crash dies
OL,4,Cafter being hit by lorry on A1(M)
OL,6,F"We have already spoken to a number of
OL,7,Fwitnesses, but I would urge anyone
OL,8,Felse who has any information that
OL,9,Fcould assist us in our enquiries to
OL,10,Fplease get in contact."
OL,12,FThe driver of the Renault Captur
OL,13,Finvolved in the initial collision was
OL,14,Ftaken to hospital for checks.
